62. The Authority may, with the approval of the Minister,
make regulations with respect to-                          VII.
                                                                    ~~~~~~
        the form of applications for licences;
         fees for licence applications;
        the renewal, revocation or suspension of licences; and
        the maximum duration of licences;
        any other matter which it is necessary to prescribe
        pursuant to this Part.
                     PART VIII. Miscellaneous
